description: This Request for Expression of Interest (RFEOI) is released by the Government of Canada to provide an Overview of the next generation of Real Property (RP) services contracts for buildings, that will replace the existing contracts and add new ones.  This RFEOI provides industry the opportunity to understand the overall strategy and provide comments as well as signal their interest. This RFEOI is the first step leading to further engagements and formal solicitations that will be conducted under the supervision of a Fairness Monitor.
